Name: Fox Masked Girl
Phrase: Only you can save goshujin-sama. Without Miyako, the curse of Hinayashiki cannot be broken. Unable to bear the swelling curse, goshujin-sama will devour M. Nishiki.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: You are the girl from Senbon Torii after all. You really are the doll in Hinayashiki...

Name: Fox Masked Girl
Phrase: Yes. My purpose is to lead you to the Gate. I want to borrow the power of Miyako and the sorceress chosen by the black doll.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Could that possibly be Yoshino?

Name: Fox Masked Girl
Phrase: Yes. I told you in Senbon Torii, didn't I? Yoshino was chosen by the doll.

Name: Fox Masked Girl
Phrase: And you, there, who have the power of the Iridescent God.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: You mean Conductor-san?

Name: Fox Masked Girl
Phrase: You are the one who gave Miyako and Yoshino special powers. You are the one who released the Guardian of the Giant Tree and brought harmony to the world.

Name: Fox Masked Girl
Phrase: The Guardians of the Four Lands are trapped. If you don't free them, the Poison contamination will hasten.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: How did you know about Poison?

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: And, the Guardians of the Giant Trees are being held captive...
I've wondered about your identity ever since I heard you speak at Senbon Torii. Who are you> You are too detailed to be just an ordinary doll.
It is understandable that you know about Miyako and Hinayashiki. But how do you know about the Guardians of the Giant Trees being held captive and about the Divine Child of Iridescence?
The Divine Children of Iris Metro are said to not have any special powers. So how do they know what we are trying to do? You speak as if you know where we are going.

Name: Fox Masked Girl
Phrase: Live long enough, and one's knowledge grows.

Name: Fox Masked Girl
Phrase: And I know about the realm of Iris Cloud.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: What do you mean? Aren't you a doll from Hinayashiki?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Take off that mask and show me your face. If you're a doll from Hinayashiki, there's no way I wouldn't recognise you.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: I don't think she can do that. If she removes her mask, the sorcery casted on herself will be broken.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Ya have also casted a sophisticated sorcery involving cognitive disruption on Miyako. Ya don't have to lie to her.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: What do you mean?

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: The girl's body is not here. Her body must be somewhere else.

Name: Fox Masked Girl
Phrase: You are indeed a doll master. I can't believe my illusion doesn't work.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: It's not because I'm a doll master that I can see through it. I was able to see through it because I am a descendant of the original Yuuzen.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: And I didn't saw through yer illusion. What I saw was yer true identity - 'Miyabihime'.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Miyabihime...?

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: She's a living doll made by Yuuzen the First. A doll from a long time ago, made a little before the Yumiharizuki.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: She's Nene and Nana's... older sister?

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: I suppose that works.

Name: Fox Masked Girl
Phrase: I guess I can't fool Yuuzen's eyes after all...

Name: Fox Masked Girl
Phrase: That's right. I come from Nishiki in Iris Cloud. I'm a doll who was given the name Miyabihime by Yuuzen the First. I call myself Miyabi ever since I came here.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Miyabi...!?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Are you, really Miyabi?

Name: Miyabi
Phrase: It's been a long time, Miyako. How long has it been since I've spoken to you in this room?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: But why...? Miyabi should be easy to recognise, even when you're wearing a mask. No, I can tell by your scent that you have changed your whole physical appearance.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: That's the kind of sorcery she used. Maybe it was important for Miyako not to find out who she was.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: They must have placed such restrictions on her. Otherwise, there's no way a mere doll would be able to do so much.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Or rather, no matter what kind of restrictions they put on it, she couldn't have gained that much power. Miyabi, ya're not alone, are ya? There's a sorceress using ya, isn't there?

Name: Miyabi
Phrase: That's right. I have a good sorceress using me. Goshujin-sama was trying to kidnap children from outside the house, correct? A strong force is needed to stop her.

Name: Miyabi
Phrase: I had to alert the Railway Army, awaken the guardians of Senbon Torii, and so on. She did things that I could never have done on my own. Miyako has found a really good person.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Wait, Miyabi. Could it be that the sorceress who is using you is...?

Name: Miyabi
Phrase: She's a doll master named Yae. I can't tell you where she is, but she is still alive. My body is with her.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Yae-san, I knew it. I wonder if this is all a coincidence.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Maybe it's not just a coincidence. It could be fate that Yoshino and Miyako met, or that Miyako and Miyabi were able to meet again.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: And it's no coincidence that Yuuzen met Miyabihime.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yuuzen, Yoshino's happy for you. All your hard work has paid off.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Yes, it was. Ricardo was right.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: As long as one lives on, something good will happen eventually. Just live until one encounters something good.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: I'm glad I'm alive. I'm glad I met you. Miyabihime.

Name: Miyabi
Phrase: Me too, Yuuzen. You are just like Yuuzen the First. Innocent, childish, always thinking about dolls. It's like they say, blood is blood.
Miyabi, guide us. How can we free the Guardians of the Giant Trees? You said that the four guardians are trapped somewhere, where are they?

Name: Miyabi
Phrase: You have to go and collect the keys in each country, Yae said. The Key of Nishiki is already in your hands. Once you have the remaining three keys, they will show us where the guardians are hiding.

Name: Miyabi
Phrase: But be careful. Only you can free the guardians. If you die, this world ends.

Name: Miyabi
Phrase: Not only will Iris Metro perish, but Iris Cloud as well.

Name: Miyabi
Phrase: Two worlds, protected by the iridescent clouds. Should one of them is engulfed by the Mist, the other will also. The two worlds will be enveloped in ever-darkness, and the Iridescent God will lose her place.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: That's what Miyako said back in the old castle in the rain!

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Come to think of it, yes. I couldn't remember where I learnt it at all, but Miyabi taught it to me.

Name: Miyabi
Phrase: Miyako. Your work is not finished. Calm goshujin-sama and take away her suffering.

Name: Miyabi
Phrase: There's a reason why goshujin-sama doesn't want you around.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: What reason?

Name: Miyabi
Phrase: Because she is afraid of your power. Miyako has the power of both person and doll.

Name: Miyabi
Phrase: And because... she can't hurt you.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Why? Goshujin-sama has become more violent than she was then, right? Isn't she even conscious anymore?

Name: Miyabi
Phrase: She may not be conscious, but she has memories. From the moment she picked you up to the day she let you go. She has all her memories.

Name: Miyabi
Phrase: Since that woman lost her child. You are the only living child she raised. Even though she became a mist-spewing demon, she couldn't hurt you.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Right. That's convenient for us. An unexpected weakness. Maybe we can achieve victory.

Name: Miyabi
Phrase: Hmmhmm, I knew Miyako would say that. You've really become reliable. I'm happy for you as your onee-san.

Name: Miyabi
Phrase: Now, that's all I can do. Work with your new friends and calm goshujin-sama.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: The room has changed!

Name: Miyako
Phrase: This is goshujin-sama's room.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: It's very worn down...

Name: Miyako
Phrase: She went on a rampage the day I left the mansion. Miyabi and the other dolls all bought me some time.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: It's so nostalgic. She used to sing songs to us here...
--Nen-nen-korori, nen-korori.
--Nen-nen-korori, nen-korori.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Finally, ya've showed up.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: The one who tried to kidnap the children.

Name: Hinayashiki Owner
Phrase: Miyako...

Name: Hinayashiki Owner
Phrase: Miyako... why did you leave?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Because I couldn't be with goshujin-sama any longer. She said I am not a doll, I am a person. Miyabi told me.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Goshujin-sama started to harm people. That's why, Miyabi let me go.

Name: Hinayashiki Owner
Phrase: Miyabi...

Name: Hinayashiki Owner
Phrase: Where is Miyabi?

Name: Hinayashiki Owner
Phrase: I've lost so many dolls because of her. My children have turned into demons!

Name: Miyako
Phrase: It was goshujin-sama who turned the dolls into demons.'

Name: Miyako
Phrase: But it's alright. I'll restore everyone to their original state. I'll return this Hinayashiki to the quiet place it used to be.

Name: Hinayashiki Owner
Phrase: How can you?

Name: Hinayashiki Owner
Phrase: HOW DO WE GET THE CHILDREN TO COME HOOOOOOOOOOME!?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: It will all be solved when you go to eternal sleep.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: Miyako, I'll help you.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yoshino will help you. Goshujin-sama too, and all the dolls in the house.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Yes. Thank you.
